snippet: Ben Crane shot a five-under 65 to open a six-stroke lead in the St. Jude Classic in Memphis before heavy rain delayed play twice and led to the suspension of the round.
abstract: Ben Crane opens six-stroke lead in the St Jude Classic before play is suspended due to rain; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Ben Crane shot a five-under 65 to open a six-stroke lead in the St. Jude Classic in Memphis before heavy rain delayed play twice and led to the suspension of the round.

headline.main: Rain Delay With Crane Leading in Memphis
